pydantic-core (2.16.3-0ubuntu1~ppa1~noble1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Initial packaging of pydantic-core 2.16.3 for the Avalan PPA.
  * Transitive runtime dep of pydantic (Avalan's `server` extra).
    Noble does not carry pydantic-core; Debian sid ships 2.46.3-1
    but its Build-Depends pull librust-* crate versions Noble does
    not match (pyo3 0.28, regex 1.11.3, hashbrown 0.16, ...).
  * Pin 2.16.3 because that release uses pyo3 0.20.2, the same
    pyo3 version Noble's python3-maturin 1.3.2 understands; later
    pydantic-core releases moved to pyo3 0.21+ which maturin 1.3
    cannot build.
  * Build with python3-maturin against a vendored cargo registry
    populated at prepare-dep-source time so dpkg-buildpackage stays
    offline.

 -- Avalan Packaging Team <avalan@avalan.ai>  Thu, 21 May 2026 10:00:00 -0300
